| >!Run for The Great Escape
| by David Thomas, © 2020

Obey <Obey$Dir>.!Boot

Set Alias$GtEscapeRMLoad IfThere %%*0 Then RMLoad %%*0

RMEnsure UtilityModule  3.50 Error The Great Escape requires RISC OS 3.5 or later

RMEnsure WindowManager  3.98 Error The Great Escape requires WindowManager 3.98 or later ('nested WIMP')

RMEnsure UtilityModule  3.70 RMEnsure CallASWI 0.02 GtEscapeRMLoad System:Modules.CallASWI
RMEnsure UtilityModule  3.70 RMEnsure CallASWI 0.02 Error The Great Escape requires CallASWI 0.02 or later

RMEnsure FPEmulator     4.03 GtEscapeRMLoad System:Modules.FPEmulator
RMEnsure FPEmulator     4.03 Error The Great Escape requires FPEmulator 4.03 or later

RMEnsure SharedCLibrary 5.17 GtEscapeRMLoad System:Modules.CLib
RMEnsure SharedCLibrary 5.34 Error The Great Escape requires SharedCLibrary 5.34 or later

RMEnsure AppEngine      0.16 GtEscapeRMLoad <GtEscape$Dir>.AppEngine
RMEnsure AppEngine      0.16 Error The Great Escape requires AppEngine 0.16 or later

Unset Alias$GtEscapeRMLoad

WimpSlot -min 520K -max 520K
| GCC:
|WimpSlot -min 600K -max 600K

Run <GtEscape$Dir>.Resources.ResFind GtEscape

Run <GtEscape$Dir>.!RunImage %*0
